                        *****  COLORBURST  *****
                           TRUE 24 BIT COLOR!

At last!  An affordable 24 bit colorcard with high resolution and great
flexibility.  ColorBurst delivers TRUE 24 bit color with 16.8 million colors
per pixel in full overscan.  With a resolution of up to 768 x 560 pixels,
this is a professional graphics card at a consumer price.
---------------------------------------------------------
--> Note that the 560 vertical is a PAL resolution. The NTSC
--> resolution is 480, the same as the HAM-E (And the HAM-E's
--> PAL vertical resolution will go to 560 also). The suggested
--> retail price is at this time $499.00. The HAM-E, including the
--> 768 pixel output option, is still about $100.00 cheaper, or
--> $200 cheaper for the current 384 pixel version.

ColorBurst is more than just a display card.  It includes a powerful graphics
coprocessor that generates many real time video effects.
