ColorBurst is compatible with ALL Amigas, and is fully transparent allowing
your Amiga to work in normal graphics mode.  ColorBurst gives the impression
that the new graphics modes are an inbuilt part of your Amiga.  ColorBurst
connects to the RGB connector and does not tie up any ports.  Once installed
there are no switches to set.  ColorBurst is available in PAL or NTSC and is
fully GenLock compatible for extremely high quality Broadcast video.  No
special monitor is necessary.  You can use your standard Amiga monitor!
